               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) ʾOrit za-lǝdat “Genesis” (fols. 5ra-42vb), incomplete (the beginning
                     is missing) 
 II) ʾOrit za-ḍaʾat “Exodus“ (fols. 43ra-74va) 
 III)
                     ʾOrit za-lewāwǝyān “Leviticus” (fols. 74vb-100ra) 
 IV) ʾOrit za-ḫʷǝlqʷ
                     “Numbers“ (fols. 100rb-138va) 
 V) ʾOrit za-dāgǝm “Deuteronomy” (fols.
                     139ra- 170va) 
 VI) ʾOrit za-Yoseʿ “Joshua” (fols. 170vb-194vb) 
 VII)
                     ʾOrit za-masāfǝnt “Judges” (fols. 194vb-216ra) 
 VIII) ʾOrit za-Rut “Ruth”
                     (fols. 216rb-216vb), incomplete (the end missing)
 
 Additiones
                     1-2.</summary>


